      • AbstractProperty

        protected AbstractProperty(String key,
                Property.Type type,
                String name,
                W widget,
                String defaultDescription,
                boolean sensitive,
                boolean hidden)
        Creates an abstract property with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        key - the property key
        type - the type of the property, or null to use the default type of STRING
        name - the default human-readable name of the property, for error messages and labels, used when a localized name cannot be found, or null to use the property key
        widget - the widget used to interact with values of the property, or null to use the default widget
        defaultDescription - the default human-readable description of the property, used when a localized description cannot be found
        sensitive - whether the property contains sensitive information
        hidden - whether the property should be hidden from the user interface
